oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Sturgill Simpson Sailors Guide to Earth at the Ryman Auditorium (Oct 28)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Ryman Auditorium (Nashville, Tenn.); Split Fountain Printing; Woodcuts (prints); Simpson, Sturgill, 1978-;polyptychs; diptychs;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (navy and split fountain, white to blue, on white) announcing A Sailor's Guide to Earth tour with Sturgill Simpson at the Ryman Auditorium on October 28. Poster is the first part of a two part set. Poster features a woodcut of a ship and a whale.
